    <div class="about-us__image"></div>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="row justify-content-center">
            <div class="col-12 col-xl-10">
                <div class="about-us__body">
                    <h1 class="about-us__title">Join Us</h1>
                    <p class="description-paragraph">
                        <strong
                            >If you are motivated active and creative, then you
                            have come to the right place!</strong
                        >
                        <strong
                            >HOOKA TIMES is continuously looking for young
                            talents to join its growing family.<br />‍ </strong
                        >Browse our current vacancies to see if you can find a
                        matching position for your career ambitions; or simply
                        send your C.V. to
                        <a href="mailto:hr@kookatimes.me" class="link"
                            >info@hookatimes.com</a
                        >
                        and we will inform you in case a fitting post opens up.
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>
<div class="section is--vacancies">
    <div class="container">
        <div class="vacancies-list-wrap">
            <h2 class="_1-6-h2"><strong>CURRENT VACANCIES</strong></h2>
